testcase.brief: Verify that the multiple accounts generation function on GM can generate user accounts of multiple index range for the PPSK roles.
testcase.description:
Pre-Condition:
Test Procedure:
1. Configure a PPSK user role on GM. 2. Try to configure user accounts of the PPSK user role, index from 1 to 10 and 30 to 50. [result 1]
